    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Hunt Breakfast\nWESTERN AIRLINES",
      "MENU\nFresh Fruit in Season\nScrambled Eggs Hampshire\nPotatoes Colbert\nSERVED FROM THE HUNT BREAKFAST CART\nHunt Breakfast\nAssorted Breakfast Meats\nand\nDanish Pastries\nMuffins\nUnder its program to provide air travelers with the finest in-flight dining in\nAmerica, Western Airlines has developed this exclusive service.\nWestern's \"Hunt Breakfast\" is patterned after the early morning feast which is\nthe traditional climax of the English fox-hunt.\nA specially designed serving cart provides a moving buffet in the aisle to make\nindividual selection and piping-hot breakfast entrees a reality for\nthe hrst time\naloft. Another Western exclusive for your travel pleasure!\nCoffee Tea\nMilk\n11",
      "aboard a\nWESTERN AIRLINES\nHunt Breakfast Flight\nPOST CARD"
    ],
